  • java.lang.Object
    • Challenge.Entity

  • class SmartEnemy
extends Enemy
    The Smart Enemy is an enemy that will ruthless track the player and attempt to kill them at all costs, they are smart enough to walk around obstacles in their pursuit of the player.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Chuks Ajeh, Angelo Balistoy
